{"tid":2460291,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老味 食完Fluoxetine 笑到停唔到","createTime":"2021-03-24T17:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T07:37:54.000Z","uid":4672,"like":132,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"01f79757325a72ac5fd25e84828badf0a785a83d","tid":2460291,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:45:19.000Z","msg":"去政府診所睇醫生 <br />\n醫生話我有d抑鬱症狀 開咗d Fluoxetine 10mg我食<br />\n返到屋企食完飯啪咗粒<br />\n<br />\n。。。<br />\n<br />\n屌你 笑到停唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗到少少事就笑到仆街<br />\n明明on9嘢 但我係度狂笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一諗返我少少嘢笑到on99<br />\n又忍唔住笑 笑到肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你呢隻咩藥黎 我睇wiki話主要療效平復情緒 改善心情<br />\n點解到我身上效果變成大麻咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d00ceec8902e9599194a6552c82d78b3429e553","tid":2460291,"uid":387826,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:48:09.000Z","msg":"係食藥定上連登太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1c5c70fda5be846bfd437e27d80b9f776027db","tid":2460291,"uid":174339,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:51:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主唔好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c3b63844f2cdf2770e715dcf38f0a312f23a0f","tid":2460291,"uid":52087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T17:51:38.000Z","msg":"有得笑下咪幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f91a436cb7e07dd7f43e484b5e05b55e56c2517","tid":2460291,"uid":4672,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T